      "content": "that's a good start. but i want to make sure i don't get shut down by my professor for being one-sided. how should i address the counter-arguments about meritocracy or people saying it's \"unfair\" to take from those who worked hard? i want to show those views are wrong without sounding like i'm just dismissing them for no reason.",
